# Unity build/cache artifacts. The repo-root .gitignore already has these
# patterns, but they're all anchored with a leading slash (e.g. /[Ll]ibrary/),
# which only matches directly at the repo root -- it can't reach into this
# subfolder. Same class of bug as packages/citygen-core's nested obj/ dirs;
# fixed here the same way, ahead of time, before a real Unity project lands.
# (*.csproj, *.sln, *.tmp, .vs/ etc. are already unanchored at the root and
# don't need repeating here.)
/[Ll]ibrary/
/[Tt]emp/
/[Oo]bj/
/[Bb]uild/
/[Bb]uilds/
/[Ll]ogs/
/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
/[Mm]emoryCaptures/
/[Rr]ecordings/
